results.p: "Too Young" is a song by American rapper and singer Post Malone. It was officially released through Republic Records on October 9, 2015

results.t: Too Young (Sidney Lippman and Sylvia Dee song)
results.p: "Too Young" is a popular song, with music written by Sidney Lippman and lyrics by Sylvia Dee. [1] A recording of the song was released by Nat King Cole in 1951.
